---
title: Teriyaki Veggie Noodle Stir-Fry with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Peanuts
description: This stir-fry has a lot going for it. It’s simple to make, especially with our delicious sauce! It’s loaded with fresh vegetables—in fact, it’s made with more veggies than noodles. Lastly, it packs great for lunch.
